    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Greek-style melitzanes </strong>with your <strong>Greek cheese </strong>crumbled<strong> </strong>over the top and the <strong>dill salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Tear the <strong>ciabatta</strong> in half and top with a little <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Garnish the<strong> </strong>Greek-style melitzanes with the <strong>reserved chopped dill</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
